public class ExpenditureTransaction
extends org.kuali.rice.kns.bo.PersistableBusinessObjectBase

Represents a expenditure transaction for a specific fiscal year, COA code, account number, sub account number, object code, sub-object code, balance type code, object type code, fiscal accounting period, project code, organization reference ID
